_sText:
This is a small aim/fy map with dev textures, it has got soft/smooth and warm colour/shades though its a bit dark, but it looks cozy.
Theres a basement underground, and a battle arena on the surface.
This map was rushed, took about 20 minutes.
(Plus, the skybox is hdr, it looks pretty but can make some people lag if you have got less than 512mb RAM)
